  "prompt": "How long did it take for your Employment Pass or S Pass application to be processed?",
  "response": "The processing time for Employment Pass and S Pass applications in Singapore can vary based on several factors, including the submission of complete documentation and the complexity of the application. Typically:\n\n- **Employment Pass (EP)**: The processing time generally ranges from 3 weeks to 8 weeks.\n- **S Pass**: The processing time usually ranges from 1 week to 8 weeks.\n\nHowever, these timelines can be affected by various factors such as the applicant's nationality, the employer's track record, and the volume of applications being processed at any given time. It is advisable to check the latest information directly from official sources or the Ministry of Manpower (MOM) website for any updates or changes in the processing times.",
